# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LICENSE PRIVATE KEY — NEVER COMMIT.
# If this leaks, anyone can mint licenses for the product. It lives OUTSIDE the
# repo (see .claude/skills/license-keygen). These patterns are a safety net, not
# the storage location.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.private.pem
*.private.key
# The real filenames the keygen writes, in case a key is ever copied into the repo by mistake.
# (`*.private.pem` above does NOT match `license-private.pem` — different shape — so name them.)
*private*.pem
*private*.key
license-private.*
license-public.*
.insha-pos-keys/
keys/
secrets/
.env
.env.*

# Local auto-update test server (see scripts/serve-updates)
dev-updates/
preview/
